metadata.name: New Breed
metadata.description:
< New Breed >  
4251x5990px 300dpi  
Digital Illustration Procreate/Photoshop  
2022

Omphalodes nedimeae is a new species from the Mediterranean Region of Turkey in the hight mountains of of Kumluca. In this work, inbetweencosmos would like to celebrate as a metaphor of everyone in the community who’s their own new breed and the excitement of finding the calling of creation and innovation.

Thanks to my friend and fellow artist MERTCAN GÜLBEN, also a botanist who’s part of the research team of this discovery for this beautiful inspiration.
metadata.Secret message: Ray would like to thank everyone she had met in the NFT community for making her 2022 such a wonderful year with amazing art, warmth and support.
